M|email-sequence|**For detailed email type reference**: See [references/email-types.md](references/email-types.md)
M|email-sequence|1. **Hook**: First line grabs attention
M|email-sequence|2. **ctx**: Why this matters to them
M|email-sequence|3. **Value**: The useful cnt
M|email-sequence|4. **CTA**: What to do next
M|email-sequence|5. **Sign-off**: Human, warm close
M|email-sequence|- Short paragraphs (1-3 sentences)
M|email-sequence|- White space between sections
M|email-sequence|- Bullet points for scanability
M|email-sequence|- Bold for emphasis (sparingly)
M|email-sequence|- Mobile-first (most read on phone)
M|email-sequence|- Conversational, not formal
M|email-sequence|- First-person (I/we) and second-person (you)
M|email-sequence|- Active voice
M|email-sequence|- Read it out loud—does it sound human?
M|email-sequence|- 50-125 words for transactional
M|email-sequence|- 150-300 words for educational
M|email-sequence|- 300-500 words for story-driven
M|email-sequence|- Buttons for primary actions
M|email-sequence|- Links for secondary actions
M|email-sequence|- One clear primary CTA per email
M|email-sequence|- Button text: Action + outcome
M|email-sequence|**For detailed copy, personalization, and testing guidelines**: See [references/copy-guidelines.md](references/copy-guidelines.md)
M|email-sequence|```
M|email-sequence|Sequence Name: [Name]
M|email-sequence|Trigger: [What starts the sequence]
M|email-sequence|Goal: [Primary conversion goal]
M|email-sequence|Length: [Number of emails]
M|email-sequence|Timing: [Delay between emails]
M|email-sequence|Exit Conditions: [When they leave the sequence]
M|email-sequence|```
M|email-sequence|```
M|email-sequence|Email [#]: [Name/Purpose]
M|email-sequence|Send: [Timing]
M|email-sequence|Subject: [Subject line]
M|email-sequence|Preview: [Preview text]
M|email-sequence|Body: [Full copy]
M|email-sequence|CTA: [Button text] → [Link destination]
M|email-sequence|Segment/Conditions: [If applicable]
M|email-sequence|```
M|email-sequence|What to measure and benchmarks
M|email-sequence|1. What triggers entry to this sequence?
M|email-sequence|2. What's the primary goal/conversion action?
M|email-sequence|3. What do they already know about you?
M|email-sequence|4. What other emails are they receiving?
M|email-sequence|5. What's your current email performance?
